snippet.title: Toilet in Wonderland | RPG Maker Game | No Commentary
snippet.description:
"Toilet in Wonderland is an adventure game where a constipated girl named Mira explores a toilet-filled Wonderland inhabited with many wacky characters."

Game: Toilet in Wonderland
Find the game here: https://memoriesoffear.jcink.net/index.php?showtopic=56
Original creator: Team Nonsense (Translated by Memories of Fear)
Release Date: 2010
Engine: RPG Maker 2000
I do NOT own anything on this video, all credit to their respective creators.

If the creator wants me to take this down, please tell me.
もしクリエイターがこれを削除することを望むなら、私に言ってほしい。 (DeepL)

I did not realize this game was over a decade old. It's still very good to me. Mario has logged in is incredibly iconic and... yeah, this is one of my favorite RPG Maker games. 

Perhaps I should've tagged this as a horror game, but... I dunno. 

This was originally supposed to be a birthday video instead of Ib. How would have that gone I wonder.

...anyway I'm tired and just needed something simple to record since I needed to go to sleep early when I recorded this.
